data.description: Ready to move in!!  Come and relax with your favorite drink in your private pool. This house offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an outside kitchen with a bar and a huge deck to enjoy the outside Florida style living.  Ramblewood is located in a secluded area of Greenacres, yet close enough to get to the main roads.  Make this house your paradise!  Definitely South Florida living.  NO HOA.
